{
  "message": "\u2728 Add cluster status indicators to more card dropdowns (#584)\n\nAdd ClusterStatusDot to 5 more cards with custom cluster filter dropdowns:\n- LLMInference.tsx - llm-d inference card\n- GPUWorkloads.tsx - GPU workloads card\n- MLJobs.tsx - ML jobs card\n- GPUInventory.tsx - GPU inventory card\n- DeploymentProgress.tsx - deployment progress card\n\nEach card now shows green/yellow/orange/red indicators for cluster health\nstate in their cluster selector dropdowns, consistent with the unified\nCardClusterFilter component.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
